efbeb049870591e994d22122d4ab31925d6101da9273146e09b40f8076291718873e0c058f2ccf4ef6d4a6f12bbaa128fe73d25413841689ab42baa7cc50e12a  0001-Stop-using-the-event_loop-fixture-4670.patch
"
